&amp;nbsp; the&amp;nbsp; good&amp;nbsp; or&amp;nbsp; service&amp;nbsp; should&amp;nbsp; be&amp;nbsp; produced&amp;nbsp; e.g.&amp;nbsp; pollution. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;• Factor immobility which causes unemployment and inefficiency. &lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;• Imperfect information, and•Inequalities in the distribution of income and wealth.&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;arcSize=5;" vertex="1" parent="1">
